IncidentSuppNarrative.NarrativeText: Attachments -NCMEC Cybertips # 161969733, 161970038 Narrative On May 25, 2023, the Maryland State Police Computer Crimes Section /Maryland Internet Crimes Against Children Task Force received NCMEC CyberTips # 161969733, 161970038. The CyberTip, generated by IMVU, indicated that a subject was involved in online enticement of children for sexual acts. The CyberTip was assigned to TFC Burnett for investigation. The CyberTips provided the following information pertaining to the suspect: Cybertip: # 161970038 Address: Huntingtown, MD US Email Address: amoniieuell08@gmail.com Screen/User Name: smddslxtt_disabled_356728300 IP Address: 98.252.32.180 05-10-2023 20:43:00 UTC Estimated Location: Huntingtown, Maryland, US at 04-30-2023 16:24:00 UTC (Not Verified) Chat Logs: CID #342563482(17 Years Old) CID #356728300(19 Years Old) 356728300 now 342563482 Freaky ah 356728300 im serious . 342563482 Me too 356728300 jus slip ds in 356728300 come take dis virginityyyyy 342563482 Yo ah not a virgin 356728300 how u gon tell me 342563482 Cus I am 356728300 i never had no dick in me 342563482 Why you a virgin? 356728300 cs i only b 356728300 fw girls 342563482 Hmmmm 356728300 yesss 342563482 So you gay 356728300 uhh 356728300 idk wha to say 356728300 ion wan say bi Cybertip: # 161969733 Address: Huntingtown, MD US Email Address: amoniieuell08@gmail.com Screen/User Name: smddslxtt_disabled_356728300 IP Address: 98.252.32.180 05-10-2023 20:35:35 UTC Estimated Location: Huntingtown, Maryland, US at 05-06-2023 16:51:00 UTC (Not Verified) Chat Service/IM Client: www.imvu.com Chat Room Name: www.imvu.com Chat Logs: CID #355912262(17 Years Old) CID #356728300(19 Years Old) 356728300 ye 355912262 Nooo 355912262 U mean rp bend u over? 356728300 go ahead 355912262 Bends u over* 356728300 *looks back at you * 355912262 Fine ah 356728300 mmh 355912262 Smacks yo ass* 356728300 *pulls my shorts off* dont een got no panties on TFC Burnett observed that one of the users is possibly 17 and with the content, it is believed that they could be a minor. TFC Burnett conducted a query of the registration IP address (98.252.32.180) through an open source database and revealed it to be registered through Comcast and geo-locates to Chesapeake Beach, Md. TFC Burnett authored a subpoena request for the IP address through Comcast and for the email address through Google, which were submitted to the Howard County States Attorneys Office for endorsement. Based on the content, a knock and talk will be conducted in the future. Case Status OPEN / PENDING ADDITIONAL INVESTIGATION

Attachments: -Signed Comcast subpoena -Signed Google subpoena -Google subscriber information -Google letter -Comcast subscriber information -Comcast letter Narrative: On 6/8/2023, I received the signed Comcast and Google subpoena from the States Attorneys Office. They both were sent through the portals with the reference numbers, Google- #36200240, Comcast- #REQ0016781. On 6/27/2023, I received the Google subpoena return with the below information: Google Account ID: 667582444831 Name: amoni euell Given Name: amoni Family Name: euell e-Mail/Recovery e-Mail: amoniieuell08@gmail.com Created on: 2023-03-20 19:02:05 Z Terms of Service IP: 2601:14b:407e:7ba0:e4d8:54a:60ed:a410 On 6/29/2023, I received the Comcast subpoena return with the below information: Subscriber Name: LYNN HARROD Service Address: 3745 S SOLOMONS ISLAND RD,BLDG C,SAINT LEONARD, MD 206852892 Billing Address: 3745 SOLOMONS ISLAND RD,APT C,SAINT LEONARD, MD 206852983 Telephone #: (443) 532-0156, 410-000-000 Type of Service: Internet Account Number: 8299400100645279 A law enforcement search revealed the name Lynn Michelle Harrod DOB: 11/3/1964), located at the above address. A future knock and talk will be conducted. On 8/10/2023, at approximately 0820 hours, Sgt. Pitcher and I responded to 3745 S Solomons Island Road, Saint Leonard, Maryland to conduct a knock and talk. Upon arrival, we made contact with Lynn Harrods daughter, who is the mother of the suspect, Amoni Euell (W/F, DOB: 3/11/2008). We explained the reasoning why we were there and she advised that she took Amonis phone at the end of the school year because she was on social media doing things she was not supposed to. But during the time of the conversations she did have her phone. She also confirmed Amonis email (amoniieuell08@gmail.com). She was unaware that these conversations were going on or what IMVU was. We provided them an internet safety talk and explained to her the severity of limiting electronic devices to Amoni. Case closed.
